---
import BaseHead from '../../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../../../consts';
import '../../../styles/global.css';

const speculationUrls = ["/", "/post", "/categories", "/tags", "/archives"];
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN" class="scroll-smooth">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title={`${SITE_TITLE} · Gzip 对比`}
      description="对比两段文本的 Gzip 压缩率"
      speculationUrls={speculationUrls}
      speculationEagerness="moderate"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-10 text-base leading-relaxed">
      <a href="/tool" class="no-style inline-flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors mb-6">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"></polyline>
        </svg>
        返回 Tools
      </a>

      <section class="mb-6">
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">
          Gzip 压缩率对比
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          输入两段文本，实时对比它们的 Gzip 压缩率和大小
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-5 mb-5">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-5">
            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-2 block">
                文本 A
              </span>
              <textarea
                id="text-a"
                rows="10"
                placeholder="输入第一段文本..."
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-sm placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary/60 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/20 transition-colors resize-none"
              ></textarea>
            </label>
          </div>

          <div
            id="result-a"
            class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 p-4 min-h-[100px]"
          >
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">请输入文本</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-5">
            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-2 block">
                文本 B
              </span>
              <textarea
                id="text-b"
                rows="10"
                placeholder="输入第二段文本..."
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-sm placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary/60 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/20 transition-colors resize-none"
              ></textarea>
            </label>
          </div>

          <div
            id="result-b"
            class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 p-4 min-h-[100px]"
          >
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">请输入文本</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        id="comparison"
        class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-5 sm:p-6 mb-6"
      >
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 text-center">输入文本后查看对比结果</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">
          说明
        </h3>
        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-2 list-none m-0 p-0">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-slate-400">•</span>
            <span>使用浏览器原生 CompressionStream API 计算 Gzip 大小（不支持时自动降级到 fflate 库）</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-slate-400">•</span>
            <span>压缩率 = Gzip 后大小 / 原始大小（越小越好）</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-slate-400">•</span>
            <span>节省 = 1 - 压缩率（越大越好）</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-slate-400">•</span>
            <span>小文本压缩后可能变大：Gzip 有固定的封装开销（header + footer + 元数据），当原始内容很短时（例如 10B），压缩后可能变成 20-30B，这是正常现象；文本越长、重复度越高，压缩效果越明显</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />

    <script>
      import { initGzipCompare } from "../../../scripts/gzip-compare.ts";
      initGzipCompare();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
